lead_paragraph: Ubaldo Jimenez pitched seven sharp innings and the Baltimore Orioles rallied to beat the Minnesota Twins 4-2 Thursday night for a three-game sweep.

headline.print_headline: Orioles Hit 2 HRs, Rally to Beat Twins 4-2 for 3-Game Sweep
